    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。PLC逻辑是跑在本地Linux上的对吧？那NFS是作为文件共享层，AzCopy负责把数据搬出去？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
