      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画个草图：把OnPremLinux做成子图，里面放NFS节点，然后NFS连到AzCopy，AzCopy再指向执行器控制器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremLinux",
